        {
            "title": "日本據悉擬發行逾11.5萬億日圓新債為刺激計畫籌資",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"613\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4wOE2OMwaOV2avFhY0odog--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxMztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0409b63f503a6a63ff0f101d7485ac96\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，日本首相高市早苗領導的政府計畫發行比去年相應規模更多的新債，以為其經濟刺激方案籌資。此舉正值外界對日本公共財政狀況和殖利率不斷上升的擔憂持續發酵之際。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些知情人士表示，高市政府的追加預算將通過額外發行至少11.5萬億日圓(735億美元)的債券來籌資。他們還表示，財政省目前預計，本財年的稅收收入將達到創紀錄的80.7萬億日圓，並產生約3萬億日圓的盈餘可用於降低政府的借款需求。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b62fced7-83f8-308f-8db0-abc3f8527768-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此，這次新增債務規模仍遠高於一年前為資助前首相石破茂的經濟措施所需的6.7萬億日圓債券發行額。預計這份追加預算將於周五獲得內閣批准。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"613\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hSVCo_edXbyERQm7MxU7LQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxMztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7ad355ee63804f2d4147635e13460df5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan to Issue Over $73.5 Billion in New Bonds to Fund Stimulus</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
